===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|May (Masters)}}
May, who is based on the [[rival]], forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Mudkip}} and its evolved forms {{p|Marshtomp}} and {{p|Swampert}}, along with {{p|Lopunny}}, {{p|Latias}}, {{p|Blaziken}}, {{p|Wailmer}}, and {{Shiny}} {{p|Kyogre}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Aside from Wailmer and Kyogre, all of her Pokémon are capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Kyogre is capable of [[Primal Reversion]]. May became a playable sync pair on January 14, 2021.

May has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]].

